{TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 103 "I-1.  (10 points)  Use M
aple to determine how many pairs of twin primes there are between 1 an
d 10,000." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 
43 "I-2.  (10 points) Analyze the graph of     " }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> \+
" 0 "" {XPPEDIT 19 1 "f := x^4-x^3-1199999/100000*x^2-80001/20000*x+40
0001/25000;" "6#>%\"fG,,*$%\"xG\"\"%\"\"\"*$F'\"\"$!\"\"*(\"(****>\"F)
\"'++5F,F'\"\"#F,*(\"&,+)F)\"&++#F,F'F)F,*&\"',+SF)\"&+]#F,F)" }}}
